        Constructs a TestInput instance with the specified test parameters.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the test case
        radix - the radix for FPE operations
        key - the raw key data for FPE operations
        tweak - the tweak for FPE operations
        plaintext - the original plaintext and expected result of decrypting the ciphertext
        ciphertext - the original ciphertext and expected result of encrypting the plaintext
